### Encrypt the playbook file

# ansible-vault encrypt playbooks/19-local-facts1.yaml
<Give the password>

### Decrypt the playbook file
# ansible-vault decrypt playbooks/19-local-facts1.yaml
<Give the password which you used for encrypotion>

### Run the encrypted playbook file.
#  ansible-playbook playbooks/19-local-facts1.yaml  --ask-vault-pass
<Give the password which you set while encrypting>
